name: White Snow
description: Hi there! So, if you are reading this text now, it means, my profile is interesting for you. And I hope, that not just my photos will be nice for you, but you have a desire to open my soul. I am a woman, who likes everything that excite emotions, as I believe that our life is mostly valuable by emotions. I am very romantic lady. I like romantic surprises and like to do it for my beloved man. I would describe myself as an easy-going, sociable, open-minded person, who loves adventures and discover new things around the world and about getting more knowledge from this impressive world! I dream of having a happy family and give all my love and all my attention to my family. I dream to see a lot of amazing places of our world with my lovely man. I want to enjoy every minute of our happy life. I can characterise myself as a happy person, but for my happiness I just miss the main – my Darling, to share all my love, affection and tenderness with. I dream of having a happy ! family and give all my love and all my attention to my family. My heart is always open to nice people! And I hope, that you will live in my heart. Come to me, dear, I am waiting for you.
